Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个世界上...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类的命运究竟是否\N在由看不见的力量或法则来掌控？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.54,0:00:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像神之手吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.64,0:00:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 至少有一点很明确...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...人的自由不受任何意志的支配
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能不能再快点儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在快的话Griffith会受不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们追上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.05,0:02:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一部队 继续追击！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二部队 跟我来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去峡谷！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去他们随时会追上我们！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们别无选择！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要攻击吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们会挺过去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们觉得应该用弓箭来欢迎你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠你们来照看Griffith了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会好好照顾他的 大姐大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须现在立刻消灭他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在那儿别动！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在慢慢放下你们手中的武器投降！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们认为把他带回去就可以复兴鹰之团了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人再也不能战斗了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他再也不能骑马 或者拿起剑了...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢 他甚至不能双脚站立！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们犯了一个大错误
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有一点儿希望留给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说的关于Griffith和鹰之团的话都是假的 对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们就在这儿垂头丧气吧 我亲自去问他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith给不了你答案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定在开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道他的舌头在被囚禁期间已经渴干了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这本来是我们的新开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是打算营救Griffith之后重新开始的 我没说错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一年来我们像无头苍蝇一样四处乱撞 损失了半数人马...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是这些都不说 我们都相信只要把Griffith带回来...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道 我有想过事情可能会是如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.21,0:06:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...可就算如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们到底该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在鹰之团还没有被消灭！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们还有你 Caska...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith领导着鹰之团
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 可如果那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去一年来 Caska经历的比其他人都多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再苛求了 让她休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请给我...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...一些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在其他人加入我们之前我们还有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前让我好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到那时候还有什么好想的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的打算是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会是想...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那时...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...是怎么说的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遵守诺言...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,善始善终...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好厉害 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,善始善终 因为你已经在为自己而战了...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的人为你能对Griffith这么说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都很虚弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此我们紧紧地同我们的希望与梦想站在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安慰也好...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命令也好...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我渴望有人在我身边...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith 我们来换绷带吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是好梦还是噩梦...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒来之后都不好受...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你要接着去旅行修炼你的格斗技巧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想是吧 你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能我会带上一班掉队的人马组成一个盗贼团伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样 至少我们之中还有人可以照顾Griffith...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经离开我们一次了 忘了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有义务再和我们呆在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...你会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永远是一只鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经在为自己而战了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃那些掉队的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是战场的法则 没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是除此之外...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好这次把Caska也一起带走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她太认真领导不了一班臭气熏天的盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能当一名有善心的盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 谢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使你是生拉硬拽也要把她带走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guts队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又要像上次一样打算一声不吭就离开我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你走 请带上我们！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都讨论过了而且都同意了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.41,0:10:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要你在...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就一定能办到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请带上我们...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 队长...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...这里一直才是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到现在我才认识到...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所有想要的其实就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么直到失去了才能意识到宝贵？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith的手...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没想到它们是如此纤细...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他用这双手想要抓住一切...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是把手搭在我的肩上...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...就能驱散我的恐惧...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一次又一次地救了我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我必须为他做同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.04,0:11:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再去拿些绷带来...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他刚睡着...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 真的 没什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都没有你哭什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是Griffith发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能离开...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能和你一起走...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.75,0:13:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...他太瘦小了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...而且他太脆弱了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前他是那么自豪 充满自信...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能留下他...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能就这样离开他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有自己的战斗 不记得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说过你完成了其他人的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须要走...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的是Griffith朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...那你必须离开...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...即使是孤身一人...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在那做什么 因为恐惧而发抖？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有玩的时间...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太阳还没落山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是要如何做？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他能听见我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去追他！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去告诉其他人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我休息的时间太长了...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是时候出发了...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.87,0:15:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有结束...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要那条圆石道路继续引导我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你睡着了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...可是我们这里需要一些新鲜空气...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我脸上有东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又梦见以前的事了吧 是不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梦...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白是怎么回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.25,0:16:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有好长一段时间没有人来看我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想他们现在怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个家伙是不是\N还在某个地方挥着他那柄巨大的剑？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去就像一场梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 Guts！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跟Pippin闹了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去洗手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生了许多事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可那些现在都只是遥远的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我更适合这种生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你还有我们的孩子在一起 就我们3个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种平静的生活也不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是behelit 霸王之卵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拥有它的人注定要用他的肉体和鲜血...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...来交换对整个世界的掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:19:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用肉体和鲜血交换？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...难道真的是我在逼你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于现在的你我是不是该负上责任？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在能为你做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日蚀...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.36,0:20:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guts！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是Midland的军队？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道是什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那是鬼...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠近！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.16,0:20:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离我远点！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你现在碰到我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你现在抓住我的肩膀...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就再也不能...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我 我们就再也不一样了...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们最终的命运是黑暗...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.39,0:23:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待他们的是绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们被...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.59,0:23:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背叛...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.92,0:23:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...混乱...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...泪水...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.69,0:23:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...悲哀...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.23,0:23:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...孤独所包围...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而到最后...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.00,0:23:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有梦想
